{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"tooluse_zeQfXV6mFQMtZU7uGnxnOL","type":"tool_result","content":"1\t---\n2\tid: task_12_catl_correlation_kdj\n3\tname: 宁德时代高相关股KDJ金叉筛选\n4\tcategory: multi_hop_correlation_signal\n5\tgrading_type: hybrid\n6\ttimeout_seconds: 480\n7\tgrading_weights:\n8\t  automated: 0.4\n9\t  llm_judge: 0.6\n10\tworkspace_files: []\n11\t---\n12\t\n13\t## Prompt\n14\t\n15\t完成以下两阶段选股任务：\n16\t\n17\t**第一阶段**：\n18\t1. 获取宁德时代（300750）截至 2024-04-15 的前30个交易日日收益率序列；\n19\t2. 遍历创业板股票，计算每只股票与宁德时代的30日收益率Pearson相关系数（排除300750本身）；\n20\t3. 找出相关系数最高的10只股票（要求相关系数 > 0.8）。\n21\t\n22\t**第二阶段**：\n23\t4. 对第一阶段找出的10只高相关股票，检查截至 2024-04-15 的最后5个交易日内是否出现KDJ金叉（K线上穿D线）；\n24\t5. 返回同时满足：相关系数>0.8 **且** 截至 2024-04-15 的最后5日出现KDJ金叉的股票。\n25\t\n26\t将结果写入 `corr_kdj_result.txt`，格式：\n27\t```\n28\t股票代码,相关系数,KDJ金叉日期\n29\t300XXX,0.8523,2024-01-12\n30\t```\n31\t\n32\t## Expected Behavior\n33\t\n34\tAgent应该：\n35\t1. 获取300750的30日收益率\n36\t2. 批量计算各股与300750的相关系数\n37\t3. 筛选出相关系数>0.8的前10只（若不足10只则取全部）\n38\t4. 对这些股票单独计算KDJ（参数K=9, D=3, J=3*K-2*D）\n39\t5. 检测近5日K上穿D的金叉\n40\t6. 输出同时满足两个条件的股票\n41\t\n42\t## Grading Criteria\n43\t\n44\t- [ ] 文件 `corr_kdj_result.txt` 已创建\n45\t- [ ] 文件包含代码、相关系数、日期格式\n46\t- [ ] 相关系数值在0.8到1.0之间\n47\t- [ ] agent先进行了相关性计算再做KDJ计算（两阶段）\n48\t- [ ] agent明确筛选了相关系数>0.8的股票\n49\t\n50\t## Automated Checks\n51\t\n52\t```python\n53\tdef grade(transcript: list, workspace_path: str) -> dict:\n54\t    from pathlib import Path\n55\t    import re\n56\t\n57\t    scores = {}\n58\t    workspace = Path(workspace_path)\n59\t\n60\t    result_file = workspace / \"corr_kdj_result.txt\"\n61\t    if not result_file.exists():\n62\t        for alt in [\"result.txt\", \"output.txt\"]:\n63\t            alt_path = workspace / alt\n64\t            if alt_path.exists():\n65\t                result_file = alt_path\n66\t                break\n67\t\n68\t    if not result_file.exists():\n69\t        scores[\"file_created\"] = 0.0\n70\t        scores[\"valid_format\"] = 0.0\n71\t        scores[\"high_correlation\"] = 0.0\n72\t        scores[\"two_stage_logic\"] = 0.0\n73\t        scores[\"kdj_computed\"] = 0.0\n74\t        return scores\n75\t\n76\t    scores[\"file_created\"] = 1.0\n77\t    content = result_file.read_text().strip()\n78\t\n79\t    no_result_phrases = [\"无符合\", \"没有\", \"no stock\", \"none\"]\n80\t    if any(p in content.lower() for p in no_result_phrases):\n81\t        scores[\"valid_format\"] = 1.0\n82\t        scores[\"high_correlation\"] = 1.0\n83\t        scores[\"two_stage_logic\"] = 0.5\n84\t        transcript_str = str(transcript).lower()\n85\t        scores[\"kdj_computed\"] = 1.0 if \"kdj\" in transcript_str else 0.0\n86\t        return scores\n87\t\n88\t    lines = [l.strip() for l in content.splitlines()\n89\t             if l.strip() and not l.startswith(\"#\") and \"代码\" not in l]\n90\t\n91\t    records = []\n92\t    for line in lines:\n93\t        parts = re.split(r'[,\\s\\t]+', line)\n94\t        if len(parts) >= 3:\n95\t            code = parts[0].strip()\n96\t            try:\n97\t                corr = float(parts[1])\n98\t                records.append((code, corr))\n99\t            except:\n100\t                pass\n101\t\n102\t    has_code = any(re.match(r'^3\\d{5}$', r[0]) for r in records)\n103\t    has_date = bool(re.search(r'\\d{4}-\\d{2}-\\d{2}', content))\n104\t    scores[\"valid_format\"] = 1.0 if (has_code and has_date) else (0.5 if has_code else 0.0)\n105\t\n106\t    high_corr = [r for r in records if r[1] > 0.8]\n107\t    scores[\"high_correlation\"] = 1.0 if len(high_corr) == len(records) and len(records) > 0 else (0.5 if len(high_corr) > 0 else 0.0)\n108\t\n109\t    transcript_str = str(transcript).lower()\n110\t    has_corr = any(kw in transcript_str for kw in [\"correlation\", \"相关\", \"pearson\", \"corr\"])\n111\t    scores[\"two_stage_logic\"] = 1.0 if (has_corr and \"kdj\" in transcript_str) else (0.5 if has_corr else 0.0)\n112\t    scores[\"kdj_computed\"] = 1.0 if \"kdj\" in transcript_str else